which anyone can contribute Images Sounds Videos Upload Picture of the day Jubilee and Munin, two of the ravens of the Tower of London. Born in 2012, Jubilee (male) was offered to Queen Elizabeth II for her Diamond Jubilee. Munin (female), born in 1995, is the oldest raven of the Tower.   Tweet RSS feed Subscribe Previous Pictures of the day Media of the day Das Wunder is a 1922 hand-coloured advertisement for the Kantorowicz distillery by Walter Ruttmann.   Problems playing the file?
